''This page is about the potion. For the terrain feature, see [[Shallow water]] or [[Deep water]]. For the card, see [[Water card]].''
{{item
 |itemtype=Potion
 |name=Potion of Water
 |cost=1
 |weight=4.0
}}
{{flavour|A unique substance, vital for the existence of most life.}}

A '''potion of water''' tastes, as expected, "like water", and gives 60 nutrition (slightly less than consuming a [[sultana]]). However, when thrown with the [[Evaporate]] spell, it creates a 3Ã—3 cloud of steam for a few turns that will damage enemies and block LOS.

[[Transmuter]]s may start with some of these, and they can be distilled from clean corpses via the spell [[Fulsome Distillation]]. When found naturally, they can easily be identified by their unique description as "clear potions."

==History==
Potions of water were removed in [[0.12]].
